<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
            margin: -30px -30px 30px -30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
        .feature-box {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .feature-box h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .role-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to {{appName}}!</h1>
            <p style="margin: 0;">Your Trusted Tender Management Platform</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
            
            <p>Congratulations! Your account has been successfully created. You're now registered as a <span class="role-badge">{{role}}</span> on our platform.</p>
            
            <h2>What's Next?</h2>
            
            {{#ifEquals role "BUYER"}}
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>üè¢ As a Buyer, you can:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Create and publish tenders</li>
                    <li>Review and evaluate bids</li>
                    <li>Manage vendor relationships</li>
                    <li>Track contract performance</li>
                    <li>Generate comprehensive reports</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/ifEquals}}
            
            {{#ifEquals role "VENDOR"}}
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>ü§ù As a Vendor, you can:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Browse available tenders</li>
                    <li>Submit competitive bids</li>
                    <li>Manage your company profile</li>
                    <li>Track payment status</li>
                    <li>Build your performance history</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/ifEquals}}
            
            {{#ifEquals role "ADMIN"}}
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3>‚öôÔ∏è As an Administrator, you can:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Manage system users and roles</li>
                    <li>Configure workflow templates</li>
                    <li>Monitor platform activities</li>
                    <li>Generate system-wide reports</li>
                    <li>Manage security settings</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/ifEquals}}
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <h3>Ready to get started?</h3>
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Login to Your Account</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-box" style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;">
                <h3>üìö Need Help?</h3>
                <p>Check out our resources:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="{{appUrl}}/help/getting-started">Getting Started Guide</a></li>
                    <li><a href="{{appUrl}}/help/faq">Frequently Asked Questions</a></li>
                    <li><a href="{{appUrl}}/contact">Contact Support</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing {{appName}} for your tender management needs.</p>
            <p>&copy; {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>